    intimacy_pressure:     'Attachment, address, care, desire, or tenderness under difficulty.',
    bodily_pressure:       'The poem is organized by pain, hunger, breath, illness, touch, or pulse.',
    death_pressure:        'Mortality, disappearance, burial, farewell, or the nearness of ending.',
    labor_pressure:        'Work, use, exhaustion, production, or being valued by function.',
